title: 189 - Don't Take This The Wrong Way
description:
Oftentimes when you’re on a journey to make your dreams come true you run into obstacles. Some obstacles are bigger than others but the most common obstacle is not having the support from the people you want it from. This could be your spouse, significant other, parents, or friends. Today on the podcast the guys discuss who and what really affects your happiness. Are you giving the responsibility of your dreams or goals to someone else? Are you depending on someone else to remain happy? Get ready to self-assess after listening to the importance of being able to esteem yourself.
